**Dubai Future Foundation**

Dubai Future Foundation drives innovation across technology, policy, education, and entrepreneurship to make Dubai a global hub for future-ready solutions. Through research, startups, accelerators, AI labs, and skill-building programs, it empowers individuals and organizations to create transformative solutions for society, government, and business. The foundation connects global experts, fosters collaboration, and implements cutting-edge initiatives to prepare for the challenges and opportunities of tomorrow.

Link: https://www.dubaifuture.ae/

